urdu transliteration text:
DUA KARO KE KOI MOJIZA DIKHAE HUSSAINPRAY THAT HUSSAIN SHOWS US A MIRACLEEnglish Transliteration
@HujjatELC
Dua Karo Ke Ko Mojiza Dikhae Hussain – Pray that Hussain shows us a miracle

Dua karo ke koi mojiza dikhae Hussain, phir ek baar hume karbala bulaae Hussain
